[resource]
script = ExtResource( 1 )
Key = "damage"
Title = "Damage"
Description = "Damage reduce a target's health. If it reaches zero, the target is knocked-out of [?combat]combat[/?].
Depending on a target's [?affinity]affinity[/?] to the [?element]element[/?] of the [?skill]skill[/?] used, it might take more or less raw damage:
[b]Resistant[/b] -50% damage
[b]Weak[/b] +100% damage

Special effects are applied after to the raw damage, for example if the actor or target have [?item]equipment[/?]:
If the actor has any weapon, the attack bonus is added to the damage.
If the target has any armor, it is substracted from the damage, the minimum being 0 damage.
(See also: [?heal]Healing[/?])"
